  "Title": "OpenClaw: Gemini OAuth exposed the PKCE verifier through the OAuth state parameter",
  "Description": "Before OpenClaw 2026.4.2, the Gemini OAuth flow reused the PKCE verifier as the OAuth `state` value. Because the provider reflected `state` back in the redirect URL, the verifier could be exposed alongside the authorization code.",
